# NestJS Project Rules

## File Naming
- Files must match pattern: ^[a-z][a-z0-9-]*\.(controller|service|module|dto|entity|guard|strategy)\.ts$
- Classes must match pattern: ^[A-Z][a-zA-Z0-9]*(Controller|Service|Module|Dto|Entity|Guard|Strategy)$

## Module Structure
- Every module must have:
  * controller.ts
  * service.ts
  * module.ts

## DTO Structure
- Every entity must have:
  * create.dto.ts
  * update.dto.ts

## Testing
- Minimum coverage: 80%
- Required tests:
  * Unit tests (*.spec.ts)
  * E2E tests (*.e2e-spec.ts)

## Documentation
- Required docs:
  * Swagger
  * README.md
  * API documentation
